  "contentHtml": "<p><strong>Chang Chang</strong>, <a href=\"https://changchangdc.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">web site</a>, <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/1200+19th+St+NW,+Washington,+DC+20036/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">1200 19th St NW, Washington, DC</a> (<a href=\"https://www.wmata.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Metro Trip Planner</a> – opens in new window)  [<a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?&amp;q=chang+chang+dc+\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Google</a> | <a href=\"https://www.washingtonian.com/100-very-best-restaurants-2024/chang-chang-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Washingtonia</a>n | <a href=\"https://www.tripadvisor.com/Restaurant_Review-g28970-d25155307-Reviews-Chang_Chang-Washington_DC_District_of_Columbia.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href=\"https://guide.michelin.com/us/en/district-of-columbia/washington-dc/restaurant/chang-chang\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Michelin</a>] </p>\n<p>Yes, the real Mama Chang, mother of Peter Chang, at 84 years old. They even <a href=\"https://tylercowensethnicdiningguide.com/index.php/mama-chang/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">named a restaurant after her</a>!</p>\n<p>It is the best Chinese meal I have eaten outside of China, and in contention for broader honors as well.</p>\n<p>Here is a photo of the menu, which says everything. There was no weak course.</p>\n<img src=\"https://tylercowensethnicdiningguide.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/MamaChang-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"853\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<p>The restaurant Chang Chang, in DC, hopes to do this again next year.</p>",
